{"tid":2340572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"觀塘兩Party Room違令營業　警拘4負責人　36名顧客遭票控罰$18萬","createTime":"2020-12-25T15:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T15:26:01.000Z","uid":224066,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2adfcbc7482ff8632419d41f7d3881c6edab12f7","tid":2340572,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201225/419122595015692288538921.jpeg/D-ajwrR5z1wDMa7NNnJnyzhhhcTzcJDLQMQai0DEGos?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201225%2F419122595015692288538921.jpeg%2FD-ajwrR5z1wDMa7NNnJnyzhhhcTzcJDLQMQai0DEGos%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=83296e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平安夜（24日）晚上約11時，觀塘警區特別職務隊、特遣隊聯同東九龍機動部隊根據線報及經深入調查後，展開反罪惡行動，警員突擊搜查分別位於興業街及鴻圖道的2個樓上單位，搗破2間懷疑正在營業的派對房間。<br />\n<br />\n行動中，警員拘捕4名本地男子，年齡介乎19歲至22歲，涉嫌違反《預防及控制疾病（規定及指示）（業務及處所）規例》（第599F章），他們現正被扣留調查。另外，房間內23名本地男子及13名本地女子，年齡介乎18至29歲，則涉嫌違反《預防及控制疾病（禁止群組聚集）條例》（第599G章），警員遂向他們發出定額罰款通知書。<br />\n<br />\n如有人違反香港法例第599G章《預防及控制疾病（禁止群組聚集）規例》，罰款金額為5,000元。至於今次行動中，36名被票控的男女，合共被罰款18萬元。警方指，在疫情嚴峻時期，警方呼籲市民顧己及人，應嚴格遵守《預防及控制疾病條例》，以協助控制疫情及減低病毒在社區傳播的風險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHX0jgW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHX0jgW.jpg&h=43cf72a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eaef7bcd68f98009310765f057928c3b81fb89bc","tid":2340572,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:09:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\">觀塘興業街</span>14號<span class=\"orange\">永興工廈</span>4樓C4室的<br />\n「Lento Party Room」派對房間舉行家族聚會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n年頭果個打邊爐群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n年頭已經響晒朵... 仲未知死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86bdd9ab05ce4e060b90b727f264d626b04fab6","tid":2340572,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zNfSFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zNfSFe.jpg&h=809270f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGKxUTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGKxUTJ.jpg&h=4fa34337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b706c49a6a0fe4dc2e440d919351ee2a5bab3e74","tid":2340572,"uid":24572,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"&quot;根據線報及經深入調查''...<br />\n報串就報串啦講到自己有做嘢咁面皮幾撚厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e33f2fd245990fd60e042c7ea3658bda9e22fe0","tid":2340572,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b706c49a6a0fe4dc2e440d919351ee2a5bab3e74","tid":2340572,"uid":24572,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"&quot;根據線報及經深入調查''...<br />\n報串就報串啦講到自己有做嘢咁面皮幾撚厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死我"},{"pid":"4d35335b28bf8b53542d54e9723cb852d7d4807c","tid":2340572,"uid":70786,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"